<inglise> REGULATION (EEC) No 1152/71 OF THE COMMISSION of 2 June 1971 on the communication of information concerning export refunds on certain agricultural products exported in the form of goods not covered by Annex II to the Treaty </inglise>
<eesti> KOMISJONI M&Auml;&Auml;RUS (EM&Uuml;) nr 1152/71 milles k&auml;sitletakse teabe edastamist teatavate asutamislepingu II lisaga h&otilde;lmamata kaupadena eksporditavate p&otilde;llumajandussaaduste ja -toodete eksporditoetuste kohta 2. juuni 1971 </eesti>
<inglise> THE COMMISSION OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES, </inglise>
<eesti> EUROOPA &Uuml;HENDUSTE KOMISJON, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Economic Community; </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa Majandus&uuml;henduse asutamislepingut, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation No 120/67/EEC 1 of 13 June 1967 on the common organisation of the market in cereals, as last amended by Regulation (EEC) No 2434/70, 2 and in particular Article 24 thereof; </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 13. juuni 1967. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust nr 120/67/EM&Uuml; teraviljaturu &uuml;hise korralduse kohta, (1) viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 2434/70, (2) eriti selle artiklit 24, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation No 122/67/EEC 3 of 13 June 1967 on the common organisation of the market in eggs, as last amended by Regulation (EEC) No 436/70, 4 and in particular Article 15 thereof; </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 13. juuni 1967. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust nr 122/67/EM&Uuml; munaturu &uuml;hise korralduse kohta, (3) viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 436/70, (4) eriti selle artiklit 15, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation No 359/67/EEC 5 of 25 July 1967 on the common organisation of the market in rice, as last amended by Regulation (EEC) No 2434/70, and in particular Article 25 thereof; </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 25. juuli 1967. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust nr 359/67/EM&Uuml; riisituru &uuml;hise korralduse kohta, (5) viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 2434/70, eriti selle artiklit 25, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation No 1009/67/EEC 6 of 18 December 1967 on the common organisation of the market in sugar, as last amended by Regulation (EEC) No 1253/70, 7 and in particular Article 38 thereof; </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 18. detsembri 1967. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust nr 1009/67/EM&Uuml; suhkruturu &uuml;hise korralduse kohta, (6) viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 1253/70, (7) eriti selle artiklit 38, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation (EEC) No 804/68 8 of 27 June 1968 on the common organisation of the market in milk and milk products, as last amended by Regulation (EEC) No 1253/70, and in particular Article 28 thereof; </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 27. juuni 1968. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 804/68 piima- ja piimatooteturu &uuml;hise korralduse kohta, (8) viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 1253/70, eriti selle artiklit 28, </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the Regulations on the common organisation of the markets in the above sectors provide that the Member States and the Commission should communicate to each other information needed for their application; whereas the procedures for communicating and disseminating this information were adopted in accordance with the procedure laid down in Article 26 of Regulation No 120/67/EEC and in the corresponding Articles of the other Regulations on the common organisation of markets; </inglise>
<eesti> ning arvestades, et: k&otilde;nealustes m&auml;&auml;rustes eespool nimetatud sektorite turu &uuml;hise korralduse kohta n&auml;hakse ette, et liikmesriigid ja komisjon peaksid edastama &uuml;ksteisele nende m&auml;&auml;ruste kohaldamiseks vajaliku teabe; k&otilde;nealuse teabe edastamise ja levitamise kord on vastu v&otilde;etud m&auml;&auml;ruse nr 120/67/EM&Uuml; artiklis 26 s&auml;testatud korras ja muude &uuml;hist turukorraldust k&auml;sitlevate m&auml;&auml;ruste vastavates artiklites s&auml;testatud korras; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, so that the provisions of the Regulations on the common organisation of the market in the above sectors can be applied as effectively as possible to refunds on the agricultural products in question exported in the form of goods listed in Annexes B and C to Council Regulation (EEC) No 204/69 9 laying down general rules for granting export refunds on certain agricultural products exported in the form of goods not covered by Annex II to the Treaty and criteria for fixing the amount of such refunds, as last amended by Regulation (EEC) No 1253/70, it is necessary to make arrangements for the communication by Member States to the Commission of certain statistics; whereas this information should also be supplied in respect of the agricultural products which qualify for the system of advance payment of refunds provided for in Article 2 of Council Regulation (EEC) No 441/69 10 of 4 March 1969 laying down additional general rules for granting export refunds on products subject to a single price system, exported unprocessed or in the form of goods not covered by Annex II to the Treaty, as last amended by Regulation (EEC) No 913/71 11; Whereas the measures provided for in this Regulation are in accordance with the Opinions of the Management Committees for Cereals, for Poultrymeat and Eggs, for Sugar and for Milk and Milk Products; 1OJ No 117, 19.6.1967, p. 2269/67. </inglise>
<eesti> on vaja kehtestada kord teatava statistika edastamiseks liikmesriikidelt komisjonile, et saaks v&otilde;imalikult t&otilde;husalt kohaldada k&otilde;nealuseid eespool nimetatud sektorite turu &uuml;hist korraldust k&auml;sitlevaid m&auml;&auml;rusi nende k&otilde;nealuste p&otilde;llumajandussaaduste ja -toodete puhul, mida on eksporditud n&otilde;ukogu m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 204/69 (milles s&auml;testatakse teatavate asutamislepingu II lisas h&otilde;lmamata kaupadena eksporditavate p&otilde;llumajandussaaduste ja -toodete eksporditoetuste andmise &uuml;ldeeskirjad ja nende toetussummade kindlaksm&auml;&auml;ramise kriteeriumid, (9) viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) 1253/70) B ja C lisas loetletud kaupadena; k&otilde;nealune teave tuleks samuti esitada p&otilde;llumajandussaaduste ja -toodete puhul, mis vastavad n&otilde;ukogu 4. m&auml;rtsi 1969. aasta m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 441/69 (milles s&auml;testatakse t&auml;iendavad &uuml;ldeeskirjad teatavate t&ouml;&ouml;tlemata v&otilde;i asutamislepingu II lisas loetlemata kaupadena eksporditavatele &uuml;htsesse hinnas&uuml;steemi kuuluvatele toodetele eksporditoetuste andmise kohta, (10) viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 913/71 (11)) artiklis 2 etten&auml;htud toetuse ettemaksmise s&uuml;steemi tingimustele; </eesti>
<inglise> 2OJ No L 262, 3.12.1970, p. 1. 3OJ No L 117, 19.6.1967, p. 2293/67. 4OJ No L 55, 10.3.1970, p. 1. 5OJ No 174, 31.7.1967, p. 1. 6OJ No 308, 18.12.1967, p. 1. 7OJ No L 143, 1.7.1970, p. 1. 8OJ No L 148, 28.6.1968, p. 13. 9OJ No L 29, 5.2.1969, p. 1. 10OJ No L 59, 10.3.1969, p. 1. 11OJ No L 98, 1.5.1971, p. 43. </inglise>
<eesti> k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;rusega etten&auml;htud meetmed on koosk&otilde;las teraviljaturu, kodulinnuliha- ja munaturu, suhkruturu ning piima- ja piimatooteturu korralduskomitee arvamusega, </eesti>
<inglise> HAS ADOPTED THIS REGULATION: </inglise>
<eesti> ON VASTU V&Otilde;TNUD K&Auml;ESOLEVA M&Auml;&Auml;RUSE. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> Member States shall communicate to the Commission, not later than the fifteenth of each month, for each of the basic products listed in Annex A to Regulation (EEC) No 204/69 which are exported or are to be exported in the form of goods listed in Annexes B or C to that Regulation: (a) the quantities for which advance fixing certificates were issued in the previous month; </inglise>
<eesti> Liikmesriigid edastavad komisjonile hiljemalt iga kuu viieteistk&uuml;mnendal kuup&auml;eval iga m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 204/69 A lisas loetletud p&otilde;hitoote puhul, mis on eksporditud v&otilde;i mida eksporditakse k&otilde;nealuse m&auml;&auml;ruse B v&otilde;i C lisas loetletud kaupadena: a) kogused, mille puhul on eelmise kuu jooksul v&auml;lja antud eelkinnitussertifikaat; </eesti>
<inglise> (b) the quantities for which, in the month immediately preceding the previous month: - export refunds were granted; </inglise>
<eesti> b) kogused, mille puhul on eelmisele kuule vahetult eelneval kuul: - antud eksporditoetust, </eesti>
<inglise> - export refunds were granted under the system of advance payment of refunds provided for in Article 2 of Regulation (EEC) No 441/69. </inglise>
<eesti> - antud eksporditoetust m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 441/69 artiklis 2 etten&auml;htud toetuse ettemaksmise s&uuml;steemi alusel. </eesti>
<inglise> For the purposes of alternative (b), any refund the amount of which the competent authorities have received and made available to the party concerned shall be considered to have been granted even if it has not actually been paid or credited to the party concerned. </inglise>
<eesti> Punkti b kohaldamisel k&auml;sitatakse k&auml;ttesaaduna iga toetussummat, mille p&auml;dev asutus on saanud ja teinud asjaomasele isikule k&auml;ttesaadavaks, isegi juhul, kui summat ei ole asjaomasele isikule makstud v&otilde;i &uuml;le kantud. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> The information referred to in Article 1 shall be broken down according to the rate of refund applying to the basic product, with details in each case of the goods exported or to be exported, specified by reference to the relevant heading No(s) of the Common Customs Tariff. </inglise>
<eesti> Artiklis 1 osutatud teave esitatakse p&otilde;hitoodete suhtes kohaldatavate toetusm&auml;&auml;rade kaupa koos &uuml;ksikasjadega selle kohta, kas kaup on eksporditud v&otilde;i eksporditakse, ja viitega &uuml;hise tollitariifistiku vastava(te) le rubriiginumbri(te) le. </eesti>
<inglise> However, the description of goods falling within heading Nos 19.03 and 22.03 of the Common Customs Tariff shall consist of a reference to the category assigned to them in Annex C to Regulation (EEC) No 204/69 according to the basic products they contain and-in the case of goods falling within heading No 19.03-to their ash content referred to dry matter. </inglise>
<eesti> &Uuml;hise tollitariifistiku rubriikidesse 19.03 ja 22.03 kuuluvate kaupade kirjeldustes on siiski viide m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 204/69 C lisas vastavalt koostisesse kuuluvale p&otilde;hitootele nendele kaupadele m&auml;&auml;ratud kategooriale ja rubriiki 19.03 kuuluvate kaupade puhul kuivaine tuhasus. </eesti>
 